title: Dancing Baby LWP FREE No Ads
creator: P.Robbie Products

extendedInfo.description: There is now a Dancing Baby App not just a live wallpaper anymore, if you are interested in an app and not a live wallpaper please search for "Dancing Baby App".Requires a phone that supports live wallpapers and a user that knows how to access live wallpapers. If don't have that then don't downloadINSTRUCTIONS TO OPEN, MENU- WALLPAPER- LIVE WALLPAPERS OR LONG PRESS HOME SCREEN- WALLPAPER- LIVE WALLPAPERS. THIS REACQUIRES A PHONE THAT SUPPORTS LIVE WALLPAPERS This is a simple live wallpaper of the infamous dancing baby from the 90's. Enjoy! to open go into wallpaper settingscheck out my other apps
